{"word":"συναλίσκομαι","slug":"συναλίσκομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>συναλίσϰομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σύν\">σύν</a>, ἁλίσϰομαι</el> ‘be caught’] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <b>be taken captive together <a href='B:510 1:4'>Ac 1:4</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> Perh. in non-literal sense of be in close quarters as though confined (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ vs.\">vs.</a> 13); otherwise it is impossible to account for the variant. <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:συναλίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:συναλλάσσω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}